citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T16:33:58.000Z","msg":"香港中式酒樓根本係藍絲集中營, 執哂都冇所謂<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eRrvqS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eRrvqS</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c6468d2e5ae3f2d9ebfd58ab55614f41e977e69","tid":1865745,"uid":245713,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"19b47fdca76dc7a480170f6fd59d2df9ba25dd3d","tid":1865745,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T12:59:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.censtatd.gov.hk/FileManager/TC/UTIL_STAT_CHART/088chart02.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.censtatd.gov.hk%2FFileManager%2FTC%2FUTIL_STAT_CHART%2F088chart02.gif&h=db47211d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.censtatd.gov.hk/FileManager/TC/UTIL_STAT_CHART/088chart04.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.censtatd.gov.hk%2FFileManager%2FTC%2FUTIL_STAT_CHART%2F088chart04.gif&h=1d28289a&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T16:59:57.000Z","msg":"去到19年4月？<br />\n<br />\n定係點，btw，新既冇懶人包但有冇個數據表睇睇"},{"pid":"8de5eba67606459fb17faec2d8c9e698902ffd51","tid":1865745,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c6468d2e5ae3f2d9ebfd58ab55614f41e977e69","tid":1865745,"uid":245713,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"19b47fdca76dc7a480170f6fd59d2df9ba25dd3d","tid":1865745,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T12:59:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.censtatd.gov.hk/FileManager/TC/UTIL_STAT_CHART/088chart02.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.censtatd.gov.hk%2FFileManager%2FTC%2FUTIL_STAT_CHART%2F088chart02.gif&h=db47211d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.censtatd.gov.hk/FileManager/TC/UTIL_STAT_CHART/088chart04.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.censtatd.gov.hk%2FFileManager%2FTC%2FUTIL_STAT_CHART%2F088chart04.gif&h=1d28289a&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T16:59:57.000Z","msg":"去到19年4月？<br />\n<br />\n定係點，btw，新既冇懶人包但有冇個數據表睇睇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T17:06:47.000Z","msg":"季/年......<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n表<br />\n<a href=\"https://gia.info.gov.hk/general/202002/05/P2020020500405_336441_1_1580888756202.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2F202002%2F05%2FP2020020500405_336441_1_1580888756202.pdf&d=N89%2BOK2GKuUyahfhaKnAsoOqxcwteoRdaW8BGlJRIvY%3D&h=c79f2215\" target=\"_blank\">https://gia.info.gov.hk/general/202002/05/P2020020500405_336441_1_1580888756202.pdf</a>"}]}